Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,A
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:04.06,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I can't believe my good luck! {This line and the next two are from episode 36}{These are all good for blu-rays}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.06,0:00:07.23,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,If that coffee hadn't spilled this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:12.45,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,How... How is that possible? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.86,0:00:18.37,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Damned brat... You even knew about Stray Cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:22.41,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:28.63,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,As long as Bites the Dust remains active,\N it will automatically continue protecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:36.80,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I... I failed! {This line and the next are from episode 36}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:39.64,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-It's... It's almost time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:45.10,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,To think you made a try for my life\N using Strat Cat's air bullets...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:54.32,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Hayato, that idea never would have occurred to you\N had you not repeated this morning three... no, four times now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:57.49,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Because you've returned here for a fourth time...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:07.21,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...Bites the Dust must be fated to blow up not just Rohan, \Nbut one or more of his friends, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:13.76,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You must have told someone other than Rohan of my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:17.59,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Or perhaps they questioned you about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.59,0:01:20.47,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Who did you kill? Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.47,0:01:23.02,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Was it that puny Koichi kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.02,0:01:25.44,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Or maybe Kujo Jotaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.44,0:01:28.98,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,His death would make me {\i1}very{\i0} happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.31,0:01:31.48,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-It's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:36.11,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Allowing you to repeat this morning would be far too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:39.45,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You would undoubtedly attack me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:44.12,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I'll undo Bites the Dust once anyone after Rohan dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:51.75,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,No one can rival my Bites the Dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:56.01,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Luck is on the side of I, Kira Yoshikage! {EVERYTHING'S COMING UP KIRA BABY}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:03.39,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,That name... That name you just said...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:08.77,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Oh, did I let my real name slip? {This line is very similar to line 151 in episode 35}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:13.23,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Yes, my real name is Kira Yoshikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:17.53,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You can tell that to whomever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:20.74,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,By the way, what time is it right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:22.03,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:24.29,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I haven't said anything about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:28.79,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Since this whole thing started,\N I haven't told a single person about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:32.88,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,All I did was make a phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:38.22,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I met a guy who told me he was late from oversleeping, \Nso this time I found his number and woke him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:41.80,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,All I did was call his house this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:44.72,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,You're the one who said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:47.31,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Just now, you said it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:49.94,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,All I had to do was wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:53.69,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for him to get here without oversleeping!
