Comment: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:28.53,Main,,0,0,0,,B
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:34.17,Title Part 4,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(648,513)\pos(141,890)\fs60}Episode 37: {\fs80} Crazy Diamond is Unbreakable Part 1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:32.33,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:35.29,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,{\an8}Looks like we still got here on time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:36.71,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hold it, Okuyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:44.55,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's fate or just a huge coincidence,\N but I can't believe the name I just heard come out of that guy's mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:46.59,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I-I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:51.06,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You just yelled out the name Kira Yoshikage, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:52.56,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:55.77,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,H-How could such a coincidence...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:57.56,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,It's not a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:05:00.90,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,It wasn't fate, either! It was a gamble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:02.53,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I made a gamble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.45,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,And I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.16,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'm sure I just heard you say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:08.53,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You definitely just said that name!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:11.33,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:12.04,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.04,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:20.38,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,If you somehow happen to have the same name as him, I can instantly heal your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.76,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Th-This guy's Kira Yoshikage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:26.80,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Th-This can't be happening! \NThis is all your fault, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.93,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,H-How has it come to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:35.85,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,I need to undo Bites the Dust and keep myself protected!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:39.86,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dorararara!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:39.31,Secondary,Kira,0,0,0,,Return, Killer Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:55.29,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,It's so cold. \NI can feel the rain running down my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:58.71,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Would it kill this kid to show up on time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:07.26,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:10.18,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,It's Koichi and Mr. Jotaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:19.81,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I did it! I made it in time! I beat fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:23.32,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I have no desire for overwhelming happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:26.74,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Nor will I accept a life of utter despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:34.24,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Like a plant that grows unperturbed in the sunlight, \NI want to live out my life in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:36.20,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You've finally shown your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:40.21,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,, I'll see to it that you're never at peace again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:45.92,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Guess Rohan hit the fuckin' jackpot with this photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:49.80,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I don't think the two of us \Nrunning into him was a coincidence, Okuyasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:55.18,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I don't know what's going on, but the fact that \Nhe said his real name to Kawajiri Hayato just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:57.81,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...makes me think we got here right in the nick of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:08.07,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Just to make sure there isn't a misunderstanding here, \NI never ran away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:12.78,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I could have killed you at any time had I so desired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:19.37,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I only refrained because I detest direct conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:25.29,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Direct conflict is completely at odds\N with the peaceful life I yearn for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:33.09,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Winning a single battle is easy,\Nbut it creates stress from anticipating subsequent fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:34.60,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,It's utterly foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:38.39,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Fighting against others is a sad and endless cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:42.14,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Half the reason we started looking for you\N is because you killed Shigechi, dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:49.32,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,A murderin' pig fucker like you ain't got no right \Nt'choose what he is or ain't gonna do, ya dumb fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:55.74,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Careful, Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:59.33,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Don't touch Killer Queen's dirty fuckin' hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:03.75,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,That's the only reason I haven't eliminated you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:08.80,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You three are currently the only obstacles standing between me and lifelong peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:12.34,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I have no choice but to fight you for uncovering my identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:17.05,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Hey, Kawajiri Hayato! Get behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:22.31,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Crazy Diamond has an effective range of one to two meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:25.27,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Its ability is to restore things which have been damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:28.44,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I won't need to use its ability against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:31.07,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I just gotta kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:41.16,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:46.42,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:49.96,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,He's strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:54.34,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,All right! I can't see what's going on, b-but he's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.39,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,He made Kira spit blood and go flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:59.14,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You're way too slow for me, Killer Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:04.69,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Trying to live a peaceful life has made you super lazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:10.07,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Your Stand just isn't cut out for one-on-one battles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:12.82,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Josuke, don't underestimate him just 'cause he's slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:20.79,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Since we gotta fight him without touchin' him, The Hand'll take care of him no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:22.83,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:27.54,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,So he can teleport things by erasing space?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:32.55,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,The direction of my attack is no longer aimed at Josuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:35.80,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,It's aimed at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:38.55,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-Inside my backpack...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:43.56,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.65,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Well, this works, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.90,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I managed to hit him with this attack on my first try.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:57.86,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,H-He didn't touch me... \NI didn't see him touch me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:01.95,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,The air... The air breathed fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:03.91,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Okuyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:09.54,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Th-The air... breathed fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:10.63,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,The air!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:15.01,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I've been keeping this plant around \Nin case something like this happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:22.89,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Now I can combine Stray Cat's ability to control air \Nwith Killer Queen's ability to create explosions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:26.14,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Hayato, I have you to thank for bringing it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:29.81,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Invisible air bubbles combined with unstoppable explosions!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:35.36,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Could two things be any more compatible than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:37.78,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,That's why he's been keeping it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:41.12,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,It's all my fault for bringing it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:44.79,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I already told you that luck is on my side, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:48.29,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,The characters in the word fate mean "luck" and "life."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:51.58,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,How fitting!
Comment: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:54.00,Main,,0,0,0,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:05.06,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Mr. Jotaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:07.98,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:11.81,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I thought I heard Josuke's voice over the rain for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:15.48,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,That useless layabout probably overslept.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:17.65,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,If they aren't here in five minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:22.53,Main,Rohan,0,0,0,,...I'm going to head to Kawajiri Hayato's school without them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:27.79,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'm coming to heal you, Okuyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.62,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I can't let you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:35.00,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Before you get to him, I'm going to blow you away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:37.42,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,It shot out air like a bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:40.55,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,And... he turned it into a bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:44.39,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,It's coming! You have to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:48.93,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Can't you see it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:50.48,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,It's that weird distorted thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:53.35,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-It's gonna hit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:54.31,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dorara!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:11:59.99,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Heal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:03.36,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,He's trying to use his ability to heal Okuyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:05.74,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,The ability to restore damaged things...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:10.25,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I'm impressed you were able to create a wall \Nfrom the broken slate so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.21,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-It's shooting again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:15.88,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:17.17,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dorarara!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:22.80,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,There's nothing worse than assuming something to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:30.18,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Especially when you have delusions of possessing great strength or abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:34.69,Main,Haya,0,0,0,,I-It's coming through the crack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:37.02,Main,Haya,0,0,0,,Even though it touched something, it didn't explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:47.70,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Hmph. I thought that was going to blow his head off, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:51.37,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...the explosion must not have been\N triggered close enough to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:56.21,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Killer Queen's bombs don't \Nautomatically detonate on contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:58.21,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,That was an inaccurate assumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:01.17,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,They can be triggered at any distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:07.26,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,No matter where you hide,\N or how quickly you protect yourself with a wall or metal plate...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:11.06,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...my bombs will pass through and explode right on top of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:15.10,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You have nowhere left to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:17.81,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:22.99,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,It's too late! There's no way he'll dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:25.70,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I have nowhere left to run?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.74,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I never planned to run away in the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:30.66,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...and I'm sure as hell not running away now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:33.75,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'm not leaving here until I heal Okuyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:36.04,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,He's running toward it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:41.92,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I-It passed by him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:46.88,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You can trigger your bombs at any distance?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:48.55,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Looks like that's not quite true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:57.27,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,If you set off an explosion while I'm close to you, Kira, you'll get caught in the blast yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:03.07,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,All right, Okuyasu! I can heal you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:06.57,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Don't touch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:12.08,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I mean, I think... \NHe could have just turned Okuyasu's body into a...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.83,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Damn! Hayato, you brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:18.04,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,No... way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:22.09,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I never saw Killer Queen touch Okuyasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:26.05,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,How do you know that, Kawajiri Hayato?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:28.34,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You're not a Stand user!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:29.47,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I can tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:32.47,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I've been living in the same house as him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.22,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,His expression totally gives him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:36.35,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,It touched him while you weren't looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:37.31,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I'm sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:39.85,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,He turned Okuyasu's body into a bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:42.61,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Kira Yoshikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:45.98,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Oh, who am I to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:51.62,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,With you charging toward me, \NI'm not sure if I actually managed to touch Okuyasu or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:54.70,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,It happened much too quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:57.70,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Should I trigger the switch and find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:02.96,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Kira Yoshikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:05.59,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Go ahead and shoot me with another air bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:08.30,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hurry up and attack me already, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:12.97,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I have no reason to recklessly attack you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:19.31,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Higashikata Josuke, I have the advantage of deciding \Nwhether to attack you or not based on the movements you make.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:24.94,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,It's very possible that I failed at turning Okuyasu into a bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:28.57,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You may still be able to heal him with Crazy Diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:36.33,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Perhaps I'm revealing too much,\N but there's only one way for you to save Okuyasu's life in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:39.08,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You have to touch and heal him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:51.97,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You'll likely explode if I succeeded at turning him into a bomb,\N but your Crazy Diamond should be able to heal him before you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:58.18,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,It's worth it to heal your best friend's \Nwounds by sacrificing yourself, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:15:59.85,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,D-Don't touch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:02.85,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I'll wait until you make your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:08.61,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Decide now whether you'll touch \Nyour best friend and heal him, or if you'll come after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:16.87,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I'll wait as long as it takes for you to make your decision,\N but I doubt you'll choose to touch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:19.37,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Even though he is your best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:24.50,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I have proof he turned him into a bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:28.34,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I'm positive he can't control more than one bomb at a time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:36.51,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Once he's used his ability to make a bomb, \Nhe can't create another one until the first goes off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:41.06,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,He would be shooting a bunch of them at once if he could, \Nbut he's only doing one at a time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:43.89,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,He turned Okuyasu into a bomb, so now he can't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.98,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:50.40,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I'm telling you that there's a way to save Okuyasu's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:51.24,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,And that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:56.11,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Killer Queen, trigger the switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:00.62,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,...if I'm the one who touches him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:03.83,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:07.58,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,H-Hayato, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:10.88,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I get it! Crazy Diamond!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:14.68,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dorararara!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:20.76,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You're insane, Kawajiri Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:23.68,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You've got guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:27.77,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Are you really just a grade-schooler, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:32.99,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,If I didn't know that you could heal people, \NI never would have done that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:35.78,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Besides, you of all people can't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:41.12,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,He'll kill me if you die, and then he'll be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:45.54,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,He'll kill my mom, too! \NThen even more people in our town!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:47.87,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,No, he has to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:54.17,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,To think that your ability is powerful enough to restore something I blew up instantaneously...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:59.51,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I realize now that your ability is a perfect counter to mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:00.97,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Killer Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:04.27,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Josuke, he's firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:14.99,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I'm going to detonate it on impact,\Nso you can't guard against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:22.66,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,However, since there's a chance you'll try to avoid it,\N I made it small and difficult to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:28.29,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I wonder if you can dodge it while carrying Okuyasu and dealing with the debris lodged in your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:30.46,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Hurry up and run away, Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:33.46,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,If his next explosion even barely touches you, you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:36.72,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Okuyasu! Your wounds are healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:38.76,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Wake up already, Okuyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:40.80,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Hurry up and move! He's gonna get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:43.22,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Eight meters until impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:46.10,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Come on, you have to wake up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:47.93,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You aren't hurt anymore, Okuyasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:48.77,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:50.35,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Seven more meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:53.77,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Just open your eyes, Okuyasu! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:57.78,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hey, Okuyasu! \NHurry up and open your eyes already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:19:02.78,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Come on! \NLet's fight together like we always do and kick his ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.91,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Josuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:11.29,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,With the same precision as Joe Montana throwing a touchdown pass, \NI'm going send the bomb right under his nose... {Araki pls}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:13.79,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,...then detonate it in his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.80,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,Four meters until impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:20.30,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,L-Let go! \NIt's gonna hit you if you don't run away! {the bomb is what will hit him}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:23.05,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Okuyasu's... Okuyasu's already{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:24.26,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:26.60,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You're the one who needs to run away, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:29.27,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,Two more meters until impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:32.81,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,The explosion will cover approximately a three-meter radius.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:38.49,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,I can see it! It's about two meters in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:40.03,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Hurry up and run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:44.49,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Okuyasu's... Okuyasu's already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:46.74,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,He isn't dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:48.25,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Okuyasu is healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:49.91,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll open his eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:53.75,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,I'll trigger the switch in one more meter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:54.75,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:19:58.84,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Dora!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:06.47,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,H-He split the air with a knife made of blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:11.94,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,Did Josuke somehow shoot a powerful stream of blood out of his body to cut it in half like a knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:18.57,Thoughts,Hayato,0,0,0,,That's right! It's just like when I used a needle to stab the air bubble \Nwhen I was first attacked by that stupid cat plant! {I know he technically calls it a "cat weed," but it's impossible not to first think "marijuana," so I just made it an insult toward Stray Cat instead.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:26.28,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,He used the blood from his wound \Nlike a water jet cutter... Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:28.37,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...to cut right through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:31.79,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I wonder if that stopped it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:35.25,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,It didn't deflate! It's headed right for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:39.71,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,The air bullets I've turned into bombs\N are kept stable by Killer Queen's ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:41.47,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,That's why it won't pop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:47.68,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Whether you cut it into pieces, \Nor try to crush it beneath your feet, my bomb ability will never go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:51.39,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,As soon as it touches you, I'll make it explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:53.39,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Finally, impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:56.52,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Huh? H-His body...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:58.40,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,...is floating?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:20:59.90,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Detonate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:03.53,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,No, it isn't floating!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:15.71,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I can't heal my own wounds with Crazy Diamond's ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:21.21,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...but since debris from the pavement got stuck in my wounds after the first explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:23.88,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,...I was able to restore them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:27.30,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Th-The piece of road inside his body dragged him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:30.93,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:34.18,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I don't know whose house this is, \Nbut we're breaking inside, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:36.94,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,Y-You need to leave Okuyasu behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:40.15,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,If you don't leave him and run, you'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:42.11,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,He'll catch up to us and kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:45.28,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Could you shut the hell up about that, Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:49.16,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Okuyasu and I are like brothers. \NHe's my best friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:51.66,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,You don't understand what I'm saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:53.91,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,By the time you healed Okuyasu's wounds, he was already dea{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:55.08,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:58.21,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't even think of finishing that sentence!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:22:00.71,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,You need to focus on defeating him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:05.84,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I don't like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:11.10,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,If not for his ability to restore things, \Nmy bombs would be unrivaled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:17.52,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,The most terrifying person standing in the way \Nof me obtaining peace of mind isn't Jotaro...
